      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "greekheb",
        "text": "κόφινος",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", the small hand-basket of the Jew, ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "Juv.",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ", iii., 14; vi., 541, probably a provision basket of considerable size, used as by the Paeonians for fishing, ",
